      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，网关是Express，加上Helmet做安全头，还有速率限制和JWT验证。这些都写进去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "gateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，网关节点已添加。接下来用户怎么连进来？",
